Blackfang sat on the table, not falling, but not fully balanced. His 
optics focus on the two bots in front of him, Rodimus and another one 
he doesn't know.

Blackfang: Is that you Rodimus? Where am I? And who might our comrade 
be? I don't know you, do I?

--- In nbwrpg@y..., Lestat Lioncourt <thevmprlestat2000@y...> wrote:
> 
> Vampirtron:
>      "It tastes like burning," He says in a kiddy voice, "For 
serious, I can't. When I had my energon overload, I went comatose. So, 
let's get to work on this, shall we?"
>  RoboRick007 wrote:: : Rodimus Prime : : Rodimus sits up on the 
table he is on. He looks over the data on the screen. Rodimus Prime: 
We help our own not leave them. If we cannot replicate a spark we'll 
have to replicate energon. The problem is that we'll have to make it 
seem like it has been processed by a Transformer, since you cant have 
raw energon, correct? OOC: Roddy came into the med bay in one of the 
"To Save A Life" posts I believe.
